To order a PacketDirect point-to-point service, first log in to the PacketFabric portal and click on the Network tab&hellip;
&hellip; and then select Packages:
Next, to add a new package, click on the plus button at the top right&hellip;
&hellip;and click SELECT PacketDirect.
Clicking the SELECT button takes us to the Select Source Port Market screen, described in the next section.
